Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This unknown Jedi was of the same unidentified species that Master Yoda belonged to. This being was a notable Jedi, as his face was carved into the wall of the Valley of the Jedi, on the planet Ruusan, along with four other Jedi.
